John Gavin Malkovich -LRB- born December 9 , 1953 -RRB- is an American actor , director , and producer .
He has appeared in more than 70 films .
For his roles in Places in the Heart and In the Line of Fire , he received Academy Award nominations .
He has also appeared in films such as Empire of the Sun , The Killing Fields , Con Air , Of Mice and Men , Rounders , Ripley 's Game , Knockaround Guys , Being John Malkovich , Shadow of the Vampire , Burn After Reading , RED , Mulholland Falls , Dangerous Liaisons , and Warm Bodies , as well as producing films such as Ghost World , Juno , and The Perks of Being a Wallflower .
In January 2017 , he launched his menswear fashion line with an online shop .